name: 透
text:
ステージの袖って
緊張感あるね
trans:
There's this kinda, um,
nervous feel in the stage wing, huh.

name: プロデューサー
trans: (Aah, she might be getting nervous herself──)

You don't need
to get so stiff.

name: プロデューサー
text: （……緊張、ほぐれたんだったらいいけど）
trans: (...if we've loosened up a little, that's good, at least.)

name: 透
text:
え？　うん
どっちかいうと柔らかいかな
trans:
Eh? Sure.
I guess I'm already feeling kinda loose, maybe?

name: プロデューサー
trans: (Haha... seems like she wasn't all that nervous.)

name: 透
text:
あー……
緊張してるってわけじゃないけど
trans:
Aah...
I wasn't really, like, getting at being nervous, though.

name: プロデューサー
text: （しまった、別の言葉をかけるべきだったか……！？）
trans: (Shoot. Maybe I should've tried saying something else...!?)
